### Scripts & Tooling
- Write utility scripts in Python, never bash, when portability matters. Do not assume `jq`, `fzf`, or other CLI tools are available.
- When writing status bars or hooks, use Python with standard library only.

### Canonical Project Paths

All projects live under `~/projects/`, organised into category folders. Never clone repos to `~/` or create project directories outside `~/projects/`.

```
~/projects/
├── engineai/       # Engine AI core products + internal tools
├── clients/        # Client delivery projects
├── personal/       # Side projects, experiments
├── tools/          # Third-party dev tools / plugins
└── archive/        # Dormant / historical
```

